name: summary
type: string (one line, up to 50 characters)
purpose: concise summary of what the test does
status: proposal

motivation:
  In order to efficiently collaborate on test maintenance it's
  crucial to have a short summary of what the test does.

stories:
  - As a developer reviewing multiple failed tests I would like
    to get quickly an idea of what my change broke.

examples: |
  summary: Test wget recursive download options
